General.Name: Tanami Gold NL
General.Description: Tanami Gold NL, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration and evaluation of gold properties in Australia. Its flagship project is the Central Tanami project covering an area of 2,211 square kilometers located in the Tanami Region of the Northern Territory. The company was incorporated in 1968 and is based in South Perth, Australia.
General.Address: 39 Mends Street, South Perth, WA, Australia, 6151
